h lessons that actually make sense.</p>
<p>For best results, watch these videos along with the Common Core Algebra =
1 Workbook. Each lesson video on this page is linked to a QR code at the to=
p-right of your math lesson in Unit 1- Building blocks of Algebra Just scan=
 and learn!</p>
<h2>Time-saving Math Resources for Teachers</h2>
<p>Need a clear way to teach and revisit like terms and binomials? Our Alge=
bra math curriculum, aligned to Common Core Math standards, is built to wor=
k seamlessly along these lesson videos. Get ready-to-use lesson materials, =
assessments, and other teacher created resources to help you save valuable =
time on lesson prep.</p>
<p>Deliver consistent, effective instruction with standard-aligned classroo=
m resources. Full access to all classroom resources is available only to ve=
rified teachers. To learn more, check out our Teacher Plus Membership here.=
</p>
